 *   form is EXACTLY `"enc1." + base64(nonce ‖ ciphertext)`.
 * - **One mapping rule everywhere** (ARCHITECTURE §8.3): JSON bodies and
 *   responses carry the `enc1.` string verbatim; the server validates only
